  Unique constraint:
  (order_item_id, user_id)
end note

legend right
  Source of truth:
  - backend/models.py
  - Alembic migrations in backend/migrations/versions

  Notes:
  - '?' means nullable or optional in the ORM
  - Enum columns are stored as strings in SQLAlchemy
  - freshfood_test.db in repo is sample data only
    and may not include the latest tables/columns
endlegend

